snippet.title: Johnny Depp & Amber Heard Abuse Claims: A Little More TRUTH!
snippet.description:
Video 1: The lies not talked about
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mN1B-H7i0nE&t=660s

Video 2: The questions you should be asking
Part 1: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NfUvMF-kkXU&t=350s
Part 2: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0G22UXfpm9s&t=648s

#johnnydepp #amberheard #metoo

Hey everyone!  Welcome back!  Or if you're here for the first time, welcome, and feel free to look around.

I am aware of all the latest happenings going on.  Between Johnny suing Amber, and her recent 292 page filing for a motion to dismiss the lawsuit, there is a lot to cover.  However, I had this video planned for weeks.  I worked on it when I could carve out the time.

This is an addendum video to my first 3 videos.  If you haven't seen those, I will link them at the top of this description.  These were discoveries and points I researched and found after completing my others and I even incorporated some of the new filings to make some important discoveries.  If you have seen my first videos, I'd greatly appreciate it if you gave this one a look too.  Thanks everyone and take care!
